| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5239 — Recovery Inhibition (donutleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fdc069b4-8d38-50ef-9ab7-ebed3c0dd6bd"
